version_description:
- Faster still photo capture.
- Support HEVC video encode.
- Revised user interface for landscape manual exposure control 
- Show Alert when memory shortage has occured.

- Enable serial shot (iOS11 and later)
- Keep zoom ratio
- Stabilized

- Keep flash settings
- Revised Video filename

- Revised User Interface
- Improve focusing while recording video
- Bug fix and Stabilized

- Support GDPR in Europe
- Fix some bug
Support New iPad Pro and Apple Watch Series 4
